<p><strong>SCP-CN-1529：</strong>猎杀夜之都市</p>
<p><strong>作者：</strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nicolasl" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3517712); return false;"><img class="small" src="https://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3517712&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1608359039" alt="NicolasL" style="background-image:url(https://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3517712)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/nicolasl" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3517712); return false;">NicolasL</a></span></p>
